network.param.modules.receipts

Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.param.modules.receipts.Order
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBean, IOrder

    public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
implements IOrder
    Implementation of IOrder, this class represents the Param order.

    This Class Document will represents order discount, order date, order items. Document defines below categories of operations:

    • setDate method to set order date.

    • setDiscount method to set order discount.

    • getDiscount method for get order discount.

    • addOrderItem method to add order item.

    • addOrderItems method to add the order items.

    • setOrderItems method to set order items.

    • getOrderItems method for get order items.

    • getDate method for get the order date.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
